<a href="../zine/0596.People.html"><img border=0 src="../hci/HdrBtnBck.gif" alt="Previous"></a><img border=0 src="../hci/H9ExDiner.gif"><a href="../zine/0596.SmallBusinessReport.html"><img border=0 src="../hci/HdrBtnNxt.gif" alt="Next"></a>

