<a href="../zine/0296.Feature.1.html"><img border=0 src="../hci/HdrBtnBck.gif" alt="Previous"></a><img border=0 src="../hci/H1Features.gif"><a href="../zine/0296.Supplement2.html"><img border=0 src="../hci/HdrBtnNxt.gif" alt="Next"></a>

